flavours. The crowning jewel though has to be the sweet, honey-glazed chermoula pork. We can’t keep our eyes or forks off it!

*Unfortunately, this
week's silverbeet was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with baby
spinach. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
